<p>Hello {{name}},</p>

<p>Your room has been assigned for your stay.</p>

<div style="background-color: #f0f0f0; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0;">
  <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;"><strong>Confirmation code:</strong> {{confirmationCode}}</p>
  <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;"><strong>Room:</strong> {{roomLabel}}</p>
  <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;"><strong>Check-in:</strong> {{formatDate checkIn}}</p>
  <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Check-out:</strong> {{formatDate checkOut}}</p>
</div>

{{#if passkeyEnabled}}
<div style="background-color: #fff4ec; border: 1px solid #ffb690; padding: 16px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0; text-align: center;">
  <p style="margin: 0 0 6px 0; color: #45464d; font-size: 13px;">Your room access code</p>
  <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; color: #9d4300;">{{passkey}}</p>
</div>
<p>Use this code to unlock your room door when you arrive.</p>
{{else}}
<p>Please use the key located in your room door.</p>
{{/if}}

<p>We look forward to welcoming you!</p>

<p>Best regards,<br/>
The Vieux Pont team</p>
